When you would use this
nltest /sc_reset:<domain>\<domain controller>?

This command is commonly used when you see errors like:
	• “The trust relationship between this workstation and the primary domain failed”
	• Authentication issues after: 
		○ Network changes
		○ VPN / site-to-site routing problems
		○ VM snapshots or restores
		○ DC availability issues
	• A machine authenticating against the wrong or remote DC
